02:30:05,400 --> 02:30:07,640
<font color="#ffffff">Ach nee, das ist ein cooler Pulli.</font>

2521
02:30:07,760 --> 02:30:08,760
<font color="#ffffff">Stockholm 2016.</font>

2522
02:30:09,040 --> 02:30:10,040
<font color="#ffffff">Du warst schon?</font>

2523
02:30:10,720 --> 02:30:11,720
<font color="#00ffff">Ich war da.</font>

