2550
02:31:34,920 --> 02:31:36,360
<font color="#ffffff">Eine megacoole Mutter.</font>

2551
02:31:36,480 --> 02:31:38,160
<font color="#ffffff">Ihr seid eine ESC-Familie</font>

2552
02:31:38,280 --> 02:31:40,200
