2645
02:37:43,960 --> 02:37:46,120
<font color="#ffffff">Glam-Orgien und Polyester-Partys,</font>

2646
02:37:46,280 --> 02:37:47,800
<font color="#ffffff">da war so viel am Start.</font>

2647
02:37:50,960 --> 02:37:53,160
<font color="#ffffff">70 Jahre Eurovision Song Contest.</font>

2648
02:37:54,040 --> 02:37:56,960
